comment:
* Abstract callback class for applications to receive updates about the Wi-Fi subsystem
     * restarting. The Wi-Fi subsystem can restart due to internal recovery mechanisms or via user
     * action.

methods.name: public abstract void onSubsystemRestarting()
methods.comment: * Indicates that the Wi-Fi subsystem is about to restart.

methods.name: public abstract void onSubsystemRestarted()
methods.comment: * Indicates that the Wi-Fi subsystem has restarted.
